items.name: ANY
desc: any cell content is valid; no conditions are used.

items.name: CUSTOM
desc: The specified formula determines which contents are valid.

items.name: DATE
desc: specifies an arithmetic series for date values.
any date value matching the specified condition is valid.

items.name: DECIMAL
desc: any number matching the specified condition is valid.

items.name: LIST
desc: Only strings from a specified list are valid.

items.name: TEXT_LEN
desc: string is valid if its length matches the specified condition.

items.name: TIME
desc: any time value matching the specified condition is valid.

items.name: WHOLE
desc: any whole number matching the specified condition is valid.
